1
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,410
♪The autumn wind slips in,
never asking when I'll return♪

2
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:27,170
♪Before the mirror,
I comb my hair, lips parted just so♪

3
00:00:28,270 --> 00:00:30,670
♪An old melody plays faintly,
perhaps the answer to this life♪

4
00:00:30,670 --> 00:00:33,780
♪If fate leaves any trace at all♪

5
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,160
♪Wild geese disappear in the woods,
flowers wither at dusk♪

6
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:41,780
♪How cruel the moonlight flooding
the empty tower, wine growing cold♪

7
00:00:42,140 --> 00:00:44,530
♪Long dreams and night rain
tearing through the heart of Luoyang♪

8
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:48,380
♪Who still rides forth
to keep a vow long left behind?♪

9
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,410
♪Paint the love and the hate♪

10
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:55,040
♪With gentle strokes of ink,
like a lone wild goose flying far away♪

11
00:00:55,810 --> 00:00:57,960
♪Frost and snow to sketch memories,
drawn taut like a bow♪

12
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,550
♪One arrow dyed in deepest red♪

13
00:00:59,550 --> 00:01:03,230
♪The bitter chill within my heart♪

14
00:01:03,890 --> 00:01:06,520
♪The sorrow falling between your brows♪

15
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Scalding memories lodged in my throat♪

16
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,290
♪Burning away the warmth we once shared♪

17
00:01:11,290 --> 00:01:13,800
♪I would fade away
with the candle's shadow♪

18
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,700
♪Sever the ties and stay behind alone♪

19
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:18,340
♪Let you go♪

20
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,240
♪Your sorrow lingers as you glance back♪

21
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:23,150
♪This longing has already worn me thin♪

22
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:26,460
♪We once vowed to grow old together♪

23
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,050
♪But if fate bears no guilt, then why♪

24
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:33,460
♪Does it play this song of tears
for me alone?♪

25
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,580
=Destiny of Love=
(Adapted from Lin Nan's novel, Destiny of Love.)

26
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:42,400
=Episode 14=

27
00:01:58,140 --> 00:01:58,750
Your Highness.

28
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:06,550
You don't need to be nervous

29
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:07,780
about meeting His Majesty.

30
00:02:08,288 --> 00:02:10,390
Let's just hope the birthday banquet
goes smoothly

31
00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:11,270
without any mistakes.

32
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:13,550
If anything goes wrong,

33
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:16,350
just blame it on me.

34
00:02:17,688 --> 00:02:18,860
Your Highness, don't worry.

35
00:02:19,333 --> 00:02:21,270
This isn't the first time
I meet His Majesty.

36
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:22,790
I will

37
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:25,460
complete my last mission

38
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:26,420
in your residence.

39
00:02:30,070 --> 00:02:31,140
It's getting late.

40
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:32,790
It will be bad if we're late.

41
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:34,740
You have always been on time.

42
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,070
Let's not become
the subject of criticism.

43
00:02:38,950 --> 00:02:40,140
It's just a family gathering.

44
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:42,700
It's alright to be late.

45
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:46,460
Let's go.

46
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,680
(Hanyuan Hall)

47
00:03:03,022 --> 00:03:04,733
- Greetings, Father.
- Greetings, Father.

48
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:05,620
You may rise.

49
00:03:06,550 --> 00:03:07,620
You've worked tirelessly

50
00:03:07,688 --> 00:03:09,022
for days on this birthday banquet.

51
00:03:09,044 --> 00:03:11,700
I'm deliberately testing you.

52
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:13,460
But don't worry.

53
00:03:13,670 --> 00:03:15,270
No matter how it turns out,

54
00:03:15,350 --> 00:03:18,293
I will only reward you.
There's no punishment.

55
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:19,790
Tell me

56
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,222
how the preparations are going.

57
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:23,990
Father.

58
00:03:24,333 --> 00:03:26,270
According
to Noble Consort's instructions,

59
00:03:26,350 --> 00:03:27,900
the emperor's birthday banquet

60
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:28,900
shouldn't be extravagant

61
00:03:28,990 --> 00:03:29,900
or lavish,

62
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:34,390
so I decided to set the core theme

63
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:36,990
as entering
the homes of ordinary people.

64
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:39,700
The main point
is to let you feel family bliss

65
00:03:39,790 --> 00:03:41,270
and affection.

66
00:03:42,270 --> 00:03:44,140
Are you saying

67
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,620
that His Majesty has never felt

68
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,900
family bliss and affection

69
00:03:48,990 --> 00:03:50,550
in the palace?

70
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,740
People might think Princess Consort Jin

71
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:56,420
is secretly sowing discord
among the imperial family.

72
00:03:57,620 --> 00:04:00,180
Father, that's not what she meant.

73
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:01,830
She's trying to say...

74
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:02,620
Father.

75
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,070
Father. Mother.

76
00:04:04,533 --> 00:04:05,830
Princess Consort Jin is saying

77
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:07,550
that Father is the sovereign.

78
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:08,740
You care for the people

79
00:04:08,830 --> 00:04:09,740
and govern leniently.

80
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,990
All sovereigns in the world
are a family.

81
00:04:12,070 --> 00:04:14,420
Speaking of family bliss and affection,

82
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:17,030
it's a joy
shared between Father and the people.

83
00:04:17,990 --> 00:04:18,710
Yes.

84
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:19,688
That's what I mean.

85
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:24,160
Alright. Tell me the details
of this birthday banquet then.

86
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,030
Details?

87
00:04:27,110 --> 00:04:29,860
Father, please look forward to it.

88
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,110
Alright.

89
00:04:45,570 --> 00:04:48,022
You want to hold the birthday banquet
in Imperial Garden?

90
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:49,030
Yes.

91
00:04:50,670 --> 00:04:52,550
Noble Consort gave us a tight budget.

92
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:54,740
Holding the birthday banquet elsewhere

93
00:04:54,820 --> 00:04:56,244
will require a lot of decorations,

94
00:04:56,288 --> 00:04:57,511
which is a thankless job.

95
00:04:58,470 --> 00:05:01,670
So I might as well hold it
in Imperial Garden,

96
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,380
and it will be in full bloom by then.

97
00:05:04,422 --> 00:05:06,350
There will be blooming flowers
and singing birds.

98
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:07,230
Won't it be beautiful?

99
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,670
Did I do something wrong?

100
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,260
No.

101
00:05:16,350 --> 00:05:17,180
No.

102
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:24,707
(Imperial Garden Layout Plan)

103
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:32,910
It's been several hours,

104
00:05:32,990 --> 00:05:34,470
and you're still looking at it.

105
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:35,790
How long do you plan to look

106
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:36,990
at this layout plan?

107
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:42,030
In principle,

108
00:05:42,110 --> 00:05:43,470
it should be fine.

109
00:05:44,177 --> 00:05:46,444
But I notice
something seems off with His Highness.

110
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:48,550
There must be something

111
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:50,155
I haven't thought of.

112
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:51,620
Alright.

113
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,380
Stop looking at it

114
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:53,350
and thinking about it.

115
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,260
Let's go eat.

116
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,300
Let's go.

117
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:56,820
Fine.

118
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:01,110
Wait.

119
00:06:09,264 --> 00:06:11,980
(Imperial Garden Layout Plan)

120
00:06:16,030 --> 00:06:17,060
I see.

121
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:20,030
Your Highness.

122
00:06:21,470 --> 00:06:22,180
I...

123
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:24,910
You didn't come out for dinner,

124
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:27,150
so I asked Jiufeng to go
to the teahouse you favor

125
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:28,150
and bought some food.

126
00:06:28,733 --> 00:06:30,300
I was just about to deliver it to you.

127
00:06:31,555 --> 00:06:32,733
Thank you, Your Highness.

128
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:35,670
I came to see you
about the birthday banquet.

129
00:06:35,910 --> 00:06:36,740
How about

130
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:39,350
we sit down and talk?

131
00:06:52,470 --> 00:06:53,180
Your Highness.

132
00:06:53,260 --> 00:06:54,380
I looked at the map

133
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:55,550
from another angle

134
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:56,740
and noticed

135
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:58,550
that Imperial Garden is long and narrow.

136
00:06:58,990 --> 00:07:01,550
There's a forest on the south side
that blocks the view

137
00:07:01,910 --> 00:07:03,500
and makes the security issue worrying.

138
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:07,380
It was rash of me to hold the banquet

139
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:08,550
in Imperial Garden.

140
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,910
Why don't we ask for permission
to enter the palace tomorrow

141
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:14,110
and tell Father

142
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:16,350
that it's better
to hold the banquet indoors?

143
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:18,550
But your performances

144
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:20,266
are all designed around Imperial Garden.

145
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:22,180
If you change it to indoors,

146
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:24,420
won't all your previous efforts
be wasted?

147
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:26,380
Besides, it's too late now.

148
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:31,110
How about

149
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:33,790
we take more precautions
on top of what we already have?

150
00:07:34,288 --> 00:07:35,377
What do you think?

151
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:37,820
I...

152
00:07:39,670 --> 00:07:40,470
I'm sorry.

153
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:42,500
What's wrong?

154
00:07:42,590 --> 00:07:43,860
I don't know.

155
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:45,670
I just wanted to

156
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:47,180
help you complete a task.

157
00:07:47,260 --> 00:07:48,800
I didn't mean to cause so much trouble.

158
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,420
I didn't expect it
to turn out like this.

159
00:07:50,420 --> 00:07:51,680
I just wanted things to go smoothly.

160
00:07:51,688 --> 00:07:52,777
Calm down first.

161
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:59,030
I used to plan everything precisely

162
00:07:59,066 --> 00:07:59,990
and demanded perfection,

163
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,860
even to the point of overcorrection.

164
00:08:02,670 --> 00:08:03,550
But later,

165
00:08:04,150 --> 00:08:05,150
I met you.

166
00:08:06,590 --> 00:08:07,500
I learned

167
00:08:07,590 --> 00:08:08,910
that no matter what happens,

168
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:12,620
we should just accept it.

169
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:19,230
You haven't eaten all day.

170
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:21,030
Hurry and eat.

171
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:22,940
Wait, Your Highness.

172
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:24,990
I'm not hungry yet.

173
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:27,030
Help me check this out first.

174
00:08:29,533 --> 00:08:31,844
(Imperial Garden Layout Plan)
How do we guard this forest?

175
00:08:31,866 --> 00:08:33,022
You just need

176
00:08:33,190 --> 00:08:35,540
to arrange the lighting
and fire prevention in this forest

177
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:37,660
and make sure no one can hide there.

178
00:08:42,933 --> 00:08:44,620
(She finally stopped
being angry with me.)

179
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:47,350
Is there anything else
that can be improved?

180
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,260
Here.

181
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,660
Listen well.

182
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:58,190
Prince Yunnuo must not know about this.

183
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,070
Do you understand?

184
00:08:59,140 --> 00:08:59,740
Yes.

185
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:05,380
Guihu.

186
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,740
Good job.

187
00:09:06,830 --> 00:09:09,430
You dare to hide things from me now.

188
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,140
I admit my wrongdoing.

189
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:13,380
Everything I did

190
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,710
was just to lighten your burden.

191
00:09:15,590 --> 00:09:17,430
Guihu, get up quickly.

192
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:21,260
Guihu.

193
00:09:23,230 --> 00:09:24,230
I know you have

194
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:26,540
always been loyal to me.

195
00:09:27,444 --> 00:09:28,977
But the country is more important.

196
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,800
We have to consider
the overall situation.

197
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:32,990
Besides, she's just an ordinary woman.

198
00:09:35,190 --> 00:09:36,260
Have you ever

199
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:39,110
wanted to protect someone?

200
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:43,350
Even if it means risking your life
and disregarding everything

201
00:09:44,430 --> 00:09:45,860
like a moth to a flame?

202
00:09:51,990 --> 00:09:52,740
Guihu.

203
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:55,380
Just let everything take its course.

204
00:09:56,350 --> 00:09:58,950
Do as I say this time.

205
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:02,470
Yes, Your Highness.

206
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:14,830
I will always wait for you.

207
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:17,830
Just like when we were little.

208
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:19,850
(Imperial Garden Layout Plan)

209
00:10:22,666 --> 00:10:24,500
I couldn't have done it
without you this time.

210
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:28,710
Thank you.

211
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:31,900
Hurry up and eat.

212
00:10:49,464 --> 00:10:51,440
(Hanyuan Hall)

213
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,230
Your Highness, let me handle this.

214
00:10:56,190 --> 00:10:57,020
This is dangerous.

215
00:10:57,110 --> 00:10:57,710
Be careful.

216
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:58,590
Don't worry.

217
00:11:09,430 --> 00:11:10,620
Hang this at the back.

218
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:11,540
Yes.

219
00:12:07,070 --> 00:12:07,990
Good job.

220
00:12:09,110 --> 00:12:09,990
It's well decorated.

221
00:12:10,310 --> 00:12:11,350
I'm very satisfied.

222
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:12,990
Jin, Princess Consort Jin.

223
00:12:13,470 --> 00:12:14,950
I'm pleased with the arrangements

224
00:12:14,950 --> 00:12:15,900
you've made.

225
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:18,020
Yunnuo is also involved.

226
00:12:18,740 --> 00:12:19,430
Yes.

227
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:20,377
Good job, Yunnuo.

228
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:22,860
Jin, do you have any other surprises

229
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:23,950
for me?

230
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:24,860
Father.

231
00:12:24,950 --> 00:12:26,500
Aliya's theme this time

232
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:28,710
is to celebrate with the people
and uniting the world.

233
00:12:29,533 --> 00:12:30,620
Celebrate with the people?

234
00:12:31,070 --> 00:12:32,710
Are you going to reward the world?

235
00:12:33,350 --> 00:12:34,660
The people will be united,

236
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:36,479
but His Majesty's treasury
would be emptied.

237
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,850
It's not about rewarding the world

238
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:40,155
but about inviting together
the best among the people

239
00:12:40,170 --> 00:12:41,955
into the palace
to celebrate with Father.

240
00:12:42,430 --> 00:12:43,620
Together?

241
00:12:43,710 --> 00:12:44,500
Well said.

242
00:12:44,590 --> 00:12:46,140
Just do as you say.

243
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:48,110
Why are you poking me?

244
00:12:49,711 --> 00:12:51,311
Let's go there and take a look.

245
00:12:51,350 --> 00:12:53,860
- Your Highness, everything is ready.
- This birthday banquet

246
00:12:53,950 --> 00:12:55,020
is well decorated.

247
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:58,140
Alright, I'm a little tired.

248
00:12:58,230 --> 00:12:59,380
I'll go back first.

249
00:12:59,470 --> 00:13:00,990
You've done a lot today.

250
00:13:01,070 --> 00:13:01,990
Go back and rest.

251
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:03,380
What?

252
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:05,140
How could this happen?

253
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:08,660
Princess Consort Jin is a princess.

254
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:09,780
I don't believe

255
00:13:09,860 --> 00:13:11,470
she would do such a treasonous thing.

256
00:13:12,190 --> 00:13:13,310
What happened?

257
00:13:14,380 --> 00:13:15,540
Nothing.

258
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:17,990
I think the palace staff
must have misunderstood.

259
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:20,310
Since it's a misunderstanding,

260
00:13:20,355 --> 00:13:21,511
there's no need to continue.

261
00:13:21,555 --> 00:13:22,830
You're easily startled.

262
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:26,660
It's about Princess Consort Jin.

263
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:28,377
I think it's better to investigate it.

264
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:42,660
I deserve death.

265
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:43,950
I deserve death.

266
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:45,110
What happened?

267
00:13:45,590 --> 00:13:46,710
Your Majesty.

268
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:47,900
I was patrolling

269
00:13:47,990 --> 00:13:49,020
and saw this young eunuch

270
00:13:49,110 --> 00:13:50,350
hiding something here secretly.

271
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:51,560
I called him,

272
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,710
yet he turned around and ran.

273
00:13:52,710 --> 00:13:53,740
So I arrested him.

274
00:13:53,830 --> 00:13:55,140
I dug out this box

275
00:13:55,350 --> 00:13:56,500
from under this tree.

276
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:59,020
The contents of this box are serious.

277
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:01,380
After inquiring him,

278
00:14:01,466 --> 00:14:04,266
I found that he acted
on the orders of Princess Consort Jin,

279
00:14:04,380 --> 00:14:06,500
so I sent someone to report it.

280
00:14:07,590 --> 00:14:08,540
What's in it?

281
00:14:13,133 --> 00:14:16,010
(Birthday on 4th day of the 10th month,
the 16th year of Luzhao Kingdom)

282
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:19,230
