284
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:25,660
Father, this has nothing to do
with Princess Consort Jin.

285
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,020
Father, calm down first.

286
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:29,830
Yunnuo, no need to rush
to beg for mercy.

287
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:33,540
Can I ask them some questions?

288
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:35,350
Go ahead.

289
00:14:35,860 --> 00:14:37,070
Ask them thoroughly for me!

290
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:44,660
When you found this eunuch
burying something,

291
00:14:44,688 --> 00:14:46,350
why didn't you report it
to Father first?

292
00:14:46,430 --> 00:14:48,620
Instead, you reported it
to Noble Consort's maid first.

293
00:14:50,350 --> 00:14:51,310
At that time,

294
00:14:53,620 --> 00:14:54,740
she happened to pass by.

295
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:55,380
So...

296
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:56,830
What a coincidence?

297
00:15:13,020 --> 00:15:14,110
You claimed

298
00:15:14,110 --> 00:15:16,380
Princess Consort Jin told you
to bury this wooden figure.

299
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:17,470
Yes.

300
00:15:18,430 --> 00:15:20,350
Did you make this wooden figure yourself

301
00:15:20,710 --> 00:15:21,990
or did she make it herself?

302
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:28,260
Her Highness made it herself.

303
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:29,430
She gave me the box,

304
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,177
but I didn't dare to open it.

305
00:15:31,555 --> 00:15:32,977
You didn't dare to open it?

306
00:15:33,230 --> 00:15:35,140
So you have no idea

307
00:15:35,230 --> 00:15:36,900
what it contained before you buried it?

308
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:38,470
Yes.

309
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:39,500
I didn't know.

310
00:15:39,590 --> 00:15:42,020
If I knew, I wouldn't bury it
even if I were beaten to death.

311
00:15:42,110 --> 00:15:43,710
Since you don't know what it contained,

312
00:15:43,780 --> 00:15:45,020
why did you run

313
00:15:45,110 --> 00:15:46,333
when the guard chased you?

314
00:15:47,740 --> 00:15:48,380
I...

315
00:15:49,070 --> 00:15:49,780
I was scared.

316
00:15:58,140 --> 00:15:59,430
What's your name?

317
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,540
Chunlai.

318
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:03,380
There are a total of 46 eunuchs
in Prince Jin's Residence.

319
00:16:03,470 --> 00:16:05,020
Why have I never seen you?

320
00:16:06,260 --> 00:16:07,110
Your Highness.

321
00:16:07,155 --> 00:16:09,200
I've been working
in Imperial Household Department.

322
00:16:09,210 --> 00:16:11,710
Her Highness met me when she
went to Imperial Household Department

323
00:16:11,710 --> 00:16:12,990
to claim her reward.

324
00:16:17,140 --> 00:16:19,053
She also gave me an emerald jade token.

325
00:16:19,066 --> 00:16:21,430
Her Highness was later
responsible for the birthday banquet.

326
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,620
This was our second meeting.

327
00:16:23,380 --> 00:16:24,660
She gave me 100 coins

328
00:16:25,470 --> 00:16:27,540
to bury the box.

329
00:16:28,590 --> 00:16:29,955
You have solid reason and proof,

330
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,380
along with time and place.

331
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:33,260
Aliya, what do you say?

332
00:16:34,590 --> 00:16:35,590
He's talking nonsense.

333
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:36,780
I've never met him.

334
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:37,620
Your Highness.

335
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:39,780
What I did for you
could've cost me my life!

336
00:16:39,860 --> 00:16:41,590
Your Highness, you must save me!

337
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:43,470
I've never seen you.

338
00:16:45,260 --> 00:16:47,710
Aliya keeps saying
that she has never seen this person.

339
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:49,020
Then why does he

340
00:16:49,088 --> 00:16:50,644
