341
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:52,600
Imperial Household Department's ledgers

342
00:16:52,644 --> 00:16:54,620
contain records of every reward.

343
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:55,830
There's no way

344
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:56,780
you can deny it.

345
00:16:58,070 --> 00:16:59,740
Are you sure that Father

346
00:16:59,830 --> 00:17:01,190
gave Aliya this jade token?

347
00:17:01,900 --> 00:17:02,710
Of course.

348
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:05,580
Father gave Aliya

349
00:17:05,670 --> 00:17:07,150
about five carts' worth of things.

350
00:17:07,340 --> 00:17:08,820
You have such a good memory.

351
00:17:08,910 --> 00:17:10,470
You even remember a small jade token.

352
00:17:11,150 --> 00:17:12,630
I manage Imperial Harem

353
00:17:12,733 --> 00:17:15,422
and remember all transactions
of Imperial Household Department.

354
00:17:15,580 --> 00:17:16,990
Do you remember

355
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:19,800
the multicolored glazed lantern
that Father bestowed upon Aliya?

356
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:21,060
Yes.

357
00:17:21,870 --> 00:17:23,710
But Father didn't give Aliya

358
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:25,020
a multicolored glazed lantern.

359
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:26,740
Looks like Her Highness' memory

360
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:28,150
isn't very accurate.

361
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:32,740
Even the sharpest memory
can fail sometimes.

362
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:35,580
Besides, what does
that multicolored glazed lantern

363
00:17:35,670 --> 00:17:37,260
have to do with today's incident?

364
00:17:37,870 --> 00:17:39,340
The brocade on this wooden figure

365
00:17:39,430 --> 00:17:40,990
is specially supplied by Xilin Kingdom.

366
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:43,870
Can Aliya explain this?

367
00:17:43,950 --> 00:17:45,430
Aliya doesn't need to explain it.

368
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:46,710
Just listen to me.

369
00:17:47,820 --> 00:17:50,190
This brocade belongs to Xilin Kingdom,

370
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:52,200
but it didn't
come from Prince Jin's Residence.

371
00:17:52,630 --> 00:17:53,820
The person who framed us

372
00:17:53,910 --> 00:17:55,150
wanted to dump all the blame

373
00:17:55,230 --> 00:17:56,500
on Aliya.

374
00:17:56,870 --> 00:17:59,230
That's why they used this brocade.

375
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:01,300
Father didn't bestow

376
00:18:01,390 --> 00:18:03,020
this brocade upon us.

377
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,740
If I remember correctly,

378
00:18:04,820 --> 00:18:05,710
I think

379
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:07,540
it was bestowed upon Imperial Harem.

380
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:12,060
Your Highness, as you said,

381
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:13,740
Imperial Household Department records

382
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:15,060
all transactions.

383
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:16,780
A quick check

384
00:18:16,888 --> 00:18:18,600
will reveal the owner of this brocade.

385
00:18:22,670 --> 00:18:25,260
Mother, I remember you told me

386
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:27,600
that there were thieves
in the inner palace.

387
00:18:27,644 --> 00:18:28,340
Hurry and check

388
00:18:28,430 --> 00:18:30,740
if this brocade
is also among the stolen goods?

389
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:32,020
Yes.

390
00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:34,630
I did lose a piece of brocade
some time ago.

391
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:36,060
I have a bad memory.

392
00:18:36,150 --> 00:18:37,377
I actually forgot about it.

393
00:18:37,780 --> 00:18:39,950
Your Highness, your mind
changes so quickly.

394
00:18:40,020 --> 00:18:40,990
Sometimes careful,

395
00:18:41,060 --> 00:18:41,950
and sometimes careless.

396
00:18:43,990 --> 00:18:44,780
How dare you?

397
00:18:44,870 --> 00:18:46,500
You falsely accused
Princess Consort Jin,

398
00:18:46,580 --> 00:18:48,020
and now you accuse me too!

399
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:48,870
Someone, come.

400
00:18:48,950 --> 00:18:49,580
Arrest him.

401
00:18:49,670 --> 00:18:50,540
- Yes.
- Yes.

402
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:51,300
I deserve to die!

403
00:18:51,390 --> 00:18:53,340
I shouldn't have wronged Her Highness!

404
00:18:53,430 --> 00:18:54,060
Stop!

405
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:55,230
I deserve to die!

406
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:57,230
I deserve to die!

407
00:18:59,260 --> 00:19:01,150
Father, you witnessed

408
00:19:01,230 --> 00:19:02,577
everything that just happened.

409
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:04,430
This guard and Chunlai's statements

410
00:19:04,540 --> 00:19:06,190
are highly inconsistent.

411
00:19:07,060 --> 00:19:08,300
Noble Consort has asked you here

412
00:19:08,300 --> 00:19:09,466
for a thorough interrogation.

413
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,540
Now that Aliya has been proven innocent,

414
00:19:11,630 --> 00:19:12,820
Aliya and I

415
00:19:12,910 --> 00:19:14,780
will continue
to plan your birthday banquet.

416
00:19:14,870 --> 00:19:15,950
The rest

417
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:17,230
is is up to you.

418
00:19:21,355 --> 00:19:23,111
