00:19:47,630 --> 00:19:48,580
I deserve to die!

423
00:19:48,670 --> 00:19:49,500
I deserve to die!

424
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:54,990
Your Highness.

425
00:19:55,630 --> 00:19:56,710
Thank you for just now.

426
00:20:02,670 --> 00:20:05,470
Do you still have
the mandarin duck handkerchief

427
00:20:05,670 --> 00:20:06,780
I embroidered for you?

428
00:20:17,580 --> 00:20:18,260
I knew my memory

429
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:19,430
isn't that bad.

430
00:20:19,733 --> 00:20:21,540
This was among the items
bestowed upon me.

431
00:20:22,780 --> 00:20:24,870
Do you know
how to cooperate with me in acting now?

432
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:29,430
You're influenced
by those you associate with.

433
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,630
Noble Consort

434
00:20:35,020 --> 00:20:36,870
can't stand a day
without causing some trouble.

435
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:38,990
My eyelid keeps twitching.

436
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:42,870
Do you think something will go wrong
at the birthday banquet?

437
00:20:43,670 --> 00:20:44,780
Why worry?

438
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:48,190
You and I are in sync now.

439
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:49,820
We're a harmonious couple.

440
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:53,630
A harmonious couple?

441
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:01,088
You really have nothing to worry.

442
00:21:02,230 --> 00:21:03,740
I will do my best

443
00:21:04,340 --> 00:21:05,230
to protect you.

444
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:09,990
But I don't want to be your burden.

445
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:12,430
You already said this before.

446
00:21:13,780 --> 00:21:15,500
You will never be my burden.

447
00:21:17,630 --> 00:21:18,670
You're my weakness.

448
00:21:20,430 --> 00:21:21,060
Then I can't...

449
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:22,260
You can't

450
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:24,540
leave my sight.

451
00:21:26,260 --> 00:21:27,740
If you really have my best interests,

452
00:21:28,540 --> 00:21:30,150
you should stay.

453
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:47,740
Let's go.

454
00:21:58,540 --> 00:22:01,150
Manman,
you weren't frightened, were you?

455
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:02,630
I want to apologize to you

456
00:22:02,710 --> 00:22:03,711
on behalf of my mother.

457
00:22:04,820 --> 00:22:05,670
It's alright.

458
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:11,580
Manman, did you come here today

459
00:22:11,670 --> 00:22:13,470
