460
00:22:17,950 --> 00:22:19,733
Prince Yunnuo, I came here to say...

461
00:22:19,850 --> 00:22:21,780
Manman, I... I know everything...

462
00:22:22,430 --> 00:22:24,430
You're always absent-minded.

463
00:22:24,500 --> 00:22:25,520
I've made the arrangements

464
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:27,000
for you to leave Prince Jin's Residence.

465
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,080
When the banquet is over...

466
00:22:28,100 --> 00:22:28,990
Prince Yunnuo.

467
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:31,910
I don't want to leave.

468
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:34,300
Manman.

469
00:22:35,230 --> 00:22:36,300
What are you talking about?

470
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:38,780
I said

471
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:41,390
I don't want to leave.

472
00:22:44,990 --> 00:22:47,950
