481
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:10,340
I'm really happy.

482
00:23:14,020 --> 00:23:14,670
Prince Yunnuo.

483
00:23:15,870 --> 00:23:17,780
I hope you'll do me this favor,

484
00:23:18,466 --> 00:23:19,844
