506
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:23,430
Contribution?

507
00:24:24,710 --> 00:24:25,630
Surprise?

508
00:24:27,100 --> 00:24:28,470
What can I come up with?

509
00:24:28,950 --> 00:24:29,780
Why don't you

510
00:24:30,910 --> 00:24:32,470
ask His Highness?

511
00:24:36,260 --> 00:24:36,910
No.

512
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:40,710
I have to come up with it myself.

513
00:24:41,990 --> 00:24:43,190
Because

514
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:45,150
