to discuss with you.

523
00:25:14,540 --> 00:25:15,340
Hurry, follow me.

524
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:15,870
This way.

525
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:16,580
Hurry.

526
00:25:16,670 --> 00:25:17,780
