00:25:27,430 --> 00:25:28,870
That's the situation.

534
00:25:29,710 --> 00:25:31,630
So what's the surprise?

535
00:25:33,670 --> 00:25:35,990
Surprise His Majesty?

536
00:25:36,540 --> 00:25:37,190
This...

537
00:25:38,511 --> 00:25:39,500
I just can't figure out

538
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:41,670
what else is there

539
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:43,300
that can surprise His Majesty.

540
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:45,870
